rows.label: xs08140100_MSG0001
rows.name: Your target was the mech all along.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140100_MSG0002
rows.name:
Oh, you're so quick!
I can see why they made you the leader.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140100_MSG0003
rows.name: And now the Vita is ours.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140100_MSG0004
rows.name: So you see? You didn't win anything—you lost.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140100_MSG0008
rows.name:
Your people managed to swipe that alien mech
out from under us, I'll give you that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140100_MSG0009
rows.name:
But our mission was to repel the invasion and defend
New LA at all costs. Nothing more, nothing less.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140100_MSG0012
rows.name:
But you—you were sent here to take the city.
And as far as I can tell, it's still standing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140100_MSG0013
rows.name: So I'd say YOU'RE the only loser here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140100_MSG0015
rows.name:
Now crawl home, tell your Ganglion leaders
you were beaten, and deliver my message.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140100_MSG0016
rows.name: Hurry up and go—before I change my mind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs08140100_MSG0019
rows.name:
It's us or you, you arrogant worm—
no negotiation, no compromise, and no mercy![ST:wait ]
